MNUMBER 155
NAME chalsuk
HUMAN
STRATEGY 301
BODY 20
SPEED 3
ATTACK1 15
DEFENSE 20
WEAPON 279 -1 100
WEAPON 683 540 100
TREASURE 1
*DESCRIPTION_START
The chalsuk is a broad-shouldered, fiendish-looking humanoid with a vaguely
snakelike face. Its thick, heavyset body and limbs are covered with wispy
brown fur so long and tangled that the creature seems much larger than it
really is. Both arms and both legs end in paws with four wide, curving claws
of a yellowish color, the same hue as the four fangs which occupy half of
its wide, gaping mouth. A small pouch hangs at its side, fashioned from the
skins of past victims and its less alert fellows.
*DESCRIPTION_END
TEXE A chalsuk walks in.
TEXM A chalsuk walks
TEXR A chalsuk hisses and backs away, retreating.
TEXF A chalsuk runs
TEXA A chalsuk leaps at
TEX1 A chalsuk bares its yellowed fangs and hisses!
TEX2 A chalsuk clenches one clawed hand into a fist.
TEX3 A chalsuk scratches at the floor with its clawed toes.
TEX4 A chalsuk's yellow eyes open wide in an angry glare.
POISON 6 2
SKINADJ 945
SKINITEM 513 -1 1 1 1
