*DESCRIPTION_START
The chalsuk guardbeast is a four-legged creature, resembling a huge, furry
rat as much as anything else. Its eyes, yellow and smaller than marbles in
an oversized, misshapen face, gleam with a savage light from beneath its
shaggy mane of brown and black hair.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
MNUMBER 157
ADJECTIVE 97
NAME elemental
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a misshapen lump of black iron, melted and hardened into a mixture
of solid metal slightly resembling an angry, leering face. The eyelike holes
near its top glow from within, a glint of polished steel in their shadows.
Arms and legs like those of an armored man protrude from places roughly
equivalent to the shoulders and hips of a human, hewn from the spirit's
substance by its living, angry energies.
*DESCRIPTION_END
