NUMBER 3500
NAME Daerik Steel, Entrance
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
The sounds of the city above filter down to this level as a steady hum and
clatter, the tread of a thousand passing boots and the buzz of a thousand
voices. Light shines down as well, throwing a few faint shadows onto the stark
concrete of the floor. The chamber is perfectly square, each wall as long and
high as the others, though the one opposite the ladder is distinguished by a
metallic circle, an opening covered with plates of curving steel. Letters
above the opening, timeworn and eroded but still partially legible,
read "Wel om  to Da r k St el."
*DESCRIPTION_END
; ladder up
ITEM 0 1108 VAL2=3523
; opening
ITEM 1 72 VAL2=3501
IFPREVERB LOOK 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The opening is blocked off by a series of curving steel plates, all spiraling in from the edges to where their points meet and mesh perfectly at the center. The entire opening resembles the iris of a gigantic gray eye. A panel glows softly on the wall beside it.
ENDIF
; panel
ITEM 2 282
IFPREVERB READ 2
  CLEARVERB
  AFFECT 3501
  EQUAL DISPLAY3501 PLRSINROOM
  ADD DISPLAY3501 MONINROOM
  AFFECT 3500
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 = 0
    EQUAL CONTAM3501 0
    ECHO PLAYER [[] Decontamination lock unoccupied []]
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER [[] 1 Animate in Decontamination lock []]
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 > 1
    STRCVT 0 DISPLAY3501
    ECHO PLAYER [[] %0 Animates in Decontamination lock []]
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  AFFECT 3501
  EQUAL DISPLAY3501 PLRSINROOM
  ADD DISPLAY3501 MONINROOM
  AFFECT 3500
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 = 0
    ECHO PLAYER [[] Decontamination lock unoccupied []]
    EQUAL CONTAM3501 0
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER [[] 1 Animate in Decontamination lock []]
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DISPLAY3501 > 1
    STRCVT 0 DISPLAY3501
    ECHO PLAYER [[] %0 Animates in Decontamination lock []]
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 1
    ECHO PLAYER The iris twists open with a faint whirring noise as you approach it.
    ECHO OTHERS The iris twists open with a faint whir as %N approaches it.
    AFFECT 3501
    ECHO OTHERS The iris twists open for a moment.
    AFFECT 3500
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER You can detect the city's usual scents here, but they are overlaid by a hint of rust and the smell of cold iron.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER You hear people walking by outside the alley above.
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL -1
  ECHO PLAYER You recall nothing about this place.
ENDIF
