*DESCRIPTION_START
The looming machines seem more and more like buildings as you look at them,
towers or fortifications on a vast and invisible city wall. The darkness which
surrounds you cloaks them as well, blurring their details and leaving only the
faintest of impressions. Your light is not strong enough to show the far end
of the refinery floor, revealing only what is close to you as you flit it
across one shape after another, wondering which ones are safe and which
present an immediate threat.
