DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
Echoes of your own breathing come back to you from all directions, changed and
lent an air of the mysterious by the unknown contours of the machinery all
around. Perhaps some of the breathing is that of another explorer in the
dark, or some native of the ancient, ruined complex. You have no way of
