Several tunnels meet here, their intersection forming a large if low-ceilinged
chamber. The floor slopes upward in only one direction, the northwest, showing
the way out while the other corridors list downwards, probably below the floor
level of the refinery outside. A smell pervades the air here, nauseating and
reminiscent of an animal's cage at the Arena. At the very center of the
intersection rests an altar, crudely constructed of painted glass.
*DESCRIPTION_END
