INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
The smashed remains of an office lie in disarray on this side of the door,
piles of ancient furnishings and rubble which was once good wall material
transformed into an uneven terrain by time and tribulations.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; door
ITEM 0 943 VAL2=3520 CLOSED UNLOCKED
