NUMBER 3522
NAME Daerik Steel, Office
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
The floor of this office is the first thing to catch your eye, a thick pile
carpet in three shades of green. No dust or dirt covers it, and it is still
intact, even twelve hundred years after the cataclysm, a wonder of the ancient
technological age. The desk and chair here are also completely intact,
untouched by the ravages of time. If you were superstitious their condition
might make you nervous, but as an experienced adventurer you remain calm.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; door
ITEM 0 943 VAl2=3519 CLOSED UNLOCKED
; desk
ITEM 1 201
; paper weight
ITEM 2 1275 ADJ1=529
; chair
ITEM 3 86

IFPREVERB LOOK 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The desk is bare, save for a weight placed at its corner.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The paperweight consists of a winged vehicle resting upon a glob of unrefined steel.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAKE 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't take that. It's scenery.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STEAL 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Go steal something else!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER What may once have been a comfortable chair is now just a wire frame. Its padding is long gone, leaving the metallic skeletal remains behind.
ENDIF

IFVERB LISTEN -1
  IFVAR RAC < 7
    ECHO PLAYER You hear nothing save your own heartbeat.
  ENDIF
ENDIF


